column2: SELECT TOP #  p.ra,p.dec, s.z,  p.dered_u, p.dered_r,   s.velDisp, s.velDispErr, p.deVRad_r, p.deVRadErr_r,  g.lgm_fib_p5#  FROM   PhotoObj AS p  JOIN SpecObj AS s ON s.bestobjid = p.objid  JOIN galSpecExtra AS g ON g.specObjID = s.bestobjid WHERE   class = &&&   AND s.z between # and #   AND s.zWarning = #  AND p.fracDeV_r > #
